â”‚   â”‚     - Displays provider-specific information like name, logo, and a link to their DNS management page (from `instructionsUrl`).
â”‚   â”‚     - Includes a "Verify My DNS Records" button (shows loading state) and a "Close" button.
â”‚   â”‚     - Uses `Dialog` component from `@/components/ui/dialog`.
