â”‚       Purpose: General type definitions for the application.
â”‚       Details: Contains `EmailSetupFormData`, `ProviderInfo`, `DnsRecord`, `InitiateEmailSetupRequest`, `InitiateEmailSetupResponse`, and other shared types. Also defines `EmailSetupDataForModal` and `DnsRecord` (for the modal in App.tsx) though these might be better co-located or in a dedicated modal types file.
â”‚       Usage: Imported by various components and functions across the project.
