â”‚   â”‚   Purpose: Allows users to select specific email campaigns they want to set up from a categorized list.
â”‚   â”‚   Details:
â”‚   â”‚   - Jungle theme, full-screen layout with a sticky image on the left and a scrollable checklist on the right. Uses the shared `@/components/Navbar`.
