â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ ğŸ“„ AuthGatePage.tsx
â”‚   â”‚   Purpose: Mandatory authentication (Sign Up or Sign In) page for guest users after they confirm their information on the InfoClarificationPage.
â”‚   â”‚   Details:
â”‚   â”‚   - Jungle theme, full-screen layout with Sign Up/Sign In forms. Uses the shared `@/components/Navbar`.
â”‚   â”‚   - No "Continue as Guest" or "Previous" option (only a "Start Over?" link to `/`).
â”‚   â”‚   - **On successful Sign Up/Sign In (`handleSubmit`):**
â”‚   â”‚     - Retrieves all `pending...` data from `localStorage` (business description, goals, campaigns, website provider, domain).
â”‚   â”‚     - Upserts this data into the `email_setups` table associated with the authenticated `user_id`. Sets `form_complete: false`.
â”‚   â”‚     - Clears the `pending...` data from `localStorage`.
â”‚   â”‚     - Navigates to `/dns-confirmation`.
â”‚   â”‚   - Handles errors with toasts. Redirects already authenticated users to the next step in the flow or dashboard.
â”‚   â”‚   Usage: Step in the multi-step onboarding flow, after `/info-clarification` (for guests) and before `/dns-confirmation`.
